Touring Tikonov is an introductory Flashpoint designed to integrate with the BattleTech Extended Tactics mods. 
Copy the mod into you BattleTech\Mods folder.

Note: This is a date secific flashpoint that activtes on 14-04-3028 and closes on 01-07-3028. You will need to have a 
saved career from before April 3028 or start a new game in 3028. Ideally, a new game is best as the Flashpoint is set up 
to be a challenge for a new Company. Established 3025 companies, or those coming off the Arano campaign will not find 
Touring Tikonov much of a challenge.

Eventually, this Flashpoint will form the foundational leg of the Operation RAT Campaign og the 4th Succession War Lore 
Pack and was used to test several concepts and provide the designer with experince with creating a Flashpoint. 

Any feedback, errors or tips for improving the Flashpoint are welcomed.


Special thanks to Victor Lapin for helping a very green modder learn some of the ins and outs of BattleTech modding.





